\n佢地都冇野可以做到 唔通放走d猶太人咩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T09:08:30.000Z","msg":"事實上你係講錯<br />\n呢單野的確唔關法官事<br />\n<br />\n你要借題發揮<br />\n然後自我感覺良好就隨便你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T09:20:35.000Z","msg":"所有權力都係來自呢個政權<br />\n警察的執法權<br />\n法官的審判權<br />\n所有被賦予權力的人都係為呢個政權服務<br />\n冇一個為呢個政權迫害香港人的人係無辜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n表面睇黎的確係唔關法官事<br />\n但當香港人因為呢d警暴問題而反抗警察<br />\n法官就將呢d反抗警察的人送入監獄<br />\n咁關唔關法官事？<br />\n定係一件事還一件事 警察犯法唔洗坐監係一件事<br />\n香港人違法反抗警察要坐監係另一件事？"},{"pid":"bceefc523f3913199578d74f551fbd29aafd56a3","tid":1914014,"uid":264245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T09:27:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec245ea02fe9caf87f5016f9d3fa8bdb5cb1d6de","tid":1914014,"uid":140924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T09:42:19.000Z","msg":"衝紅燈 &ne; 衝向市民<br />\n後者係蓄意謀殺"},{"pid":"322d2dac015aa0e455c240bb7670d4f028c2ce45","tid":1914014,"uid":140924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4fd58da8aac967f36ac9f51d87ec0d3fb08835fa","tid":1914014,"uid":256059,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b9c8e9a1d5ed41195ddf3ed89fefc200d6885cd6","tid":1914014,"uid":37869,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b2c614f6863895ee12fb49ea6ab3d0231981f084","tid":1914014,"uid":95577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T08:54:13.000Z","msg":"你咁講當值期當攞支搶鳩射都得㗎啦<br />\n試下擺單case上庭睇下個官點判<br />\n係容唔容許<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T08:55:36.000Z","msg":"法官：我判冇罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T09:00:13.000Z","msg":"根本連法庭都無機會上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/